@startuml SME_Ops_Sequence_Invite
title UC27 — Invite employee — §2.3.7

actor Owner
participant "Team UI" as Web
participant "EmployeesController" as API
participant "EmployeesService" as Svc
participant "Supabase Auth" as Auth
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

Owner -> Web : submit invite
Web -> API : POST /employees
API -> Svc : invite(dto, orgId)
Svc -> Auth : createUser(email, password)
Auth --> Svc : user id
Svc -> DB : insert User (role != OWNER)
DB --> Svc : employee
Svc --> API : employee DTO
API --> Web : 201
Web --> Owner : refresh team list

@enduml
